description.en:
AR is the utility token within the MARKYT.shop and e-commerce ecosystem all over the world!


"www.MARKYT.shop" is the e-commerce company that MAR will be used actively in the near future.

The MAR will be freely traded on crypto-exchanges.

The maximum supply cannot excess 1,000,000,000 however, 55% of the maximum supply, 550,000,000, is locked for 2 years. We believe MAR will be leading the e-commerce with the power of blockchain in the future, we are very confident that we will be a brand in the market so %55 will be reserved as locked to be used for further marketing, developments, partnerships, team and brand.
